snippet.title: Tales of the Uncanny - Reveal Trailer - New horror game
snippet.description:
Tales of the Uncanny is a horror game featuring standalone stories filled with eerie atmospheres and unsettling mysteries. Each chapter reveals a new, chilling narrative where your choices shape the outcomes. 

Dive into the unknown and embrace the uncanny.

Wishlist now on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/3281230/?utm_source=Youtube
